    metaTitle: "Botox for Excessive Sweating in Men (Hyperhidrosis) — Cost, Results & What to Expect",
    description: "Excessive sweating ruining your shirts, handshakes, and confidence? Botox for hyperhidrosis is one of the most effective treatments available for men. Here's how it works.",
