    slug: "botox-executives-professionals-men",
    title: "Botox for Male Executives and Professionals — The Career Guide",
    metaTitle: "Botox for Male Executives & Professionals — Career Advantage Guide",
    description: "High-stakes careers reward sharp, energetic appearances. Here's how male executives and professionals are using Botox strategically — and why it fits seamlessly into a demanding schedule.",
